snippet.title: Scrap Galaxy Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
Web: http://www.scrapgalaxy.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/scrapgalaxy
Tumblr: http://scrapgalaxy.tumblr.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/scrapGalaxy/

Scrap Galaxy is a local multiplayer game for up to 4 players. Each player uses a gamepad. It takes place in a galactic junkyard where the players construct their ships.

Soundtrack by Connor O.R.T. Linning
http://www.connorlinning.com/
